<h1>闪</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">shǎn</span><span class=alesi>(shan3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 闪 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 闪</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/flash" style="color:black;">flash</a>; <a href="/dictionary/avoid" style="color:black;">avoid</a>, <a href="/dictionary/dodge" style="color:black;">dodge</a>, evade</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 5<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 5 strokes: <a href="/character/他" title="ta1: other, another; he, she, it">他</a>, <a href="/character/们" title="men: adjunct pronoun indicate plural">们</a>, <a href="/character/出" title="chu1: go out, send out; stand; produce">出</a>, <a href="/character/可" title="ke3: may, can, -able; possibly">可</a>, <a href="/character/对" title="dui4: correct, right; facing, opposed">对</a>, <a href="/character/生" title="sheng1: life, living, lifetime; birth">生</a>, <a href="/character/发" title="fa1: issue, dispatch, send out; hair">发</a>, <a href="/character/用" title="yong4: use, employ, apply, operate; use">用</a>, <a href="/character/去" title="qu4: go away, leave, depart">去</a>, <a href="/character/主" title="zhu3: master, chief owner; host; lord">主</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/門" title="Kangxi radical 169">門</a>&nbsp;169.2</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/缓" title="huan3: slow, leisurely; to postpone, delay">缓</a>, <a href="/character/哲" title="zhe2: wise, sagacious; wise man, sage">哲</a>, <a href="/character/络" title="luo4: enmesh, wrap around; web, net">络</a>, <a href="/character/伟" title="wei3: great, robust; extraordinary">伟</a>, <a href="/character/甲" title="jia3: armor, shell; fingernails; 1st heavenly stem">甲</a>, <a href="/character/震" title="zhen4: shake, quake, tremor; excite">震</a>, <a href="/character/延" title="yan2: delay, postpone, defer">延</a>, <a href="/character/促" title="cu4: urge, press, hurry; close">促</a>, <a href="/character/纯" title="chun2: pure, clean, simple">纯</a>, <a href="/character/忍" title="ren3: endure, bear, suffer; forbear">忍</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List 